Knoxville appeared in the [[1890 U.S. Census]] as a village.<ref name=1910CensusGA/> It appeared in the [[1900 U.S. Census]] and the [[1910 U.S. census]]<ref name=1910CensusGA/> but was delisted in the [[1920 U.S. census]].<ref name=1930CensusGA/> It was listed as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusP2/>

